		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>Wondrous Item - Very Rare (Requires Attunement)</em></p><p><em>This fine garment is made of black silk interwoven with faint, silvery threads.</em></p><p>While wearing it, you gain the following benefits.</p><ul><li><p>You have &amp;reference[Resistance] to &amp;reference[Poison] damage.</p></li><li><p>You have a &amp;reference[Climbing]{Climb} Speed equal to your Speed and can move up, down, and across vertical surfaces and along ceilings, while leaving your hands free.</p></li><li><p>You can't be caught in webs of any sort and can move through webs as if they were &amp;reference[Difficult Terrain].</p></li><li><p>You can cast <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.QbacOEHBdmvlUYl8]{Web}</em>(save DC 13). The web created by the spell fills twice its normal area. Once used, this property can't be used again until the next dawn.</p></li></ul>",
